549
00:28:05.726 --> 00:28:08.771
Don't let your heart
close your eyes to it.

550
00:28:10.606 --> 00:28:11.774
Whoa.

551
00:28:15.486 --> 00:28:18.030
She's the only woman
I ever loved.

552
