Julian's weird.

580
00:29:42.239 --> 00:29:44.909
[phone vibrating]

581
00:29:46.994 --> 00:29:47.870
[groans]

582
00:29:47.995 --> 00:29:49.163
[vibrating continues]

583
00:29:49.288 --> 00:29:50.748
[groans]

584
