- [sighs]
- [vibrating stops]

585
00:30:02.760 --> 00:30:03.802
Oh. no. no.

586
00:30:04.887 --> 00:30:06.639
No. Oh. no!

587
00:30:06.764 --> 00:30:07.932
[line ringing]

588
00:30:08.057 --> 00:30:08.849
[tone chimes]

589
00:30:08.974 --> 00:30:09.975
<i>[automated voice] We're sorry.</i>

590
00:30:10.100 --> 00:30:12.144
