- [Gia squealing]
- [Matt] Whoa!

715
00:34:47.586 --> 00:34:50.714
Oh my-- Where am I going?
I gotta get back to the tour!

716
00:34:50.839 --> 00:34:52.382
I gotta get back to the tour.

717
00:34:52.508 --> 00:34:54.551
Whoa. [chuckles] Oh. no. no. no.

718
00:34:54.676 --> 00:34:56.345
Okay. okay. Oh.

719
