- Yeah. fine. [panting]

728
00:35:21.787 --> 00:35:23.497
Okay. Come on. Can-Can we eat?

729
00:35:23.622 --> 00:35:24.623
<i>- Okay.
- Andiamo.</i>

730
00:35:24.748 --> 00:35:27.042
Okay. Oh. wow. [straining] Okay.

731
00:35:27.167 --> 00:35:28.293
