Hey. [speaking in Italian]

739
00:35:44.142 --> 00:35:44.935
Okay.

740
00:35:45.060 --> 00:35:46.728
[speaking in Italian]

741
00:35:46.854 --> 00:35:50.107
[conversing in Italian]

742
00:35:51.817 --> 00:35:54.069
[conversing in Italian]

743
