American cash.

1069
00:48:53.598 --> 00:48:54.432
They don't.

1070
00:48:54.557 --> 00:48:56.225
No. I had to start a tab.

1071
00:48:59.812 --> 00:49:01.147
[groans] Oh. man.

1072
00:49:09.113 --> 00:49:09.947
You invited her?

1073
