I-I wonder why.

1075
00:49:17.080 --> 00:49:20.875
<i>Zoo-chero! Ciao! Ah. bravo!</i>

1076
00:49:21.000 --> 00:49:22.168
<i>Perfetto. Two kiss. mwah. mwah.</i>

1077
00:49:22.293 --> 00:49:24.379
Yeah. and I-I didn't
make it weird.

1078
00:49:24.504 --> 00:49:25.630
Long time. no see.

1079
00:49:25.755 --> 00:49:27.256
