[speaks in Italian] Let's dance.

1124
00:51:27.168 --> 00:51:28.211
Oh. go!

1125
00:51:28.336 --> 00:51:29.253
<i>Come on! Andiamo!</i>

1126
00:51:29.378 --> 00:51:30.421
No. no. no. no.

1127
