- Easy. easy. easy.
- Oh. Okay. okay.

1150
00:52:12.463 --> 00:52:14.006
- [winces]
- No. no. It's okay. No. no. no.

1151
00:52:14.131 --> 00:52:15.091
No broke.

1152
