1166
00:52:49.125 --> 00:52:53.754
[mutters] She-she go down.
She-She break her arm.

1167
00:52:54.630 --> 00:52:57.758
I was like. "Oh. I
didn't mean to.

1168
00:52:57.884 --> 00:52:59.051
- But I told you."
- Yeah.

1169
00:52:59.176 --> 00:53:00.595
[speaking in Italian]

1170
